<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>HardwareTalk - 하드웨어 커뮤니티</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #1e2a38;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
    }

    .navbar .logo {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.5em;
    }

    .navbar .auth {
      font-size: 0.95em;
    }

    .navbar a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 10px;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">🔧 HardwareTalk</div>
    <div class="auth">
      <% if (user) { %>
        <span><strong><%= user.username %></strong></span>
        <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/login">로그인</a> | <a href="/register">회원가입</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>하드웨어 커뮤니티에 오신 걸 환영합니다!</h1>
    <p>로그인하고 질문/답변을 나눠보세요!</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
